extendedInfo.description: Hidden within Dublin there are numerous, beautiful examples of native street art. This app stores the current best street art Dublin has to offer. Users can view where the street art is located in the map tab or view all the street art in the gallery. From either of these they can then choose the option of being shown how to locate the street art form their current location. This application is aimed at young tourists, who want a free and eventful stroll through the city. All the street art is located with walking distance from each other, providing an interesting and unique way to explore Dublinâs City Center.
